__________________________________________________________________________________________                             
                              Dragon Mania
__________________________________________________________________________________________
 This is very simple and very first game I made for my son Suleman. Good thing is he loved the game 
 and he master it in no time.
 This game is for ages 6-8.

 HOW TO PLAY:
1. First we need to upload to browser , either by connecting through ```live server ```, ```npm install and npm start``` or ```npxserve.```.
2. This game is designed for ```laptops```, ``` desktops```, cannot play on small devices, or ipads.
3. Once you ```Restart``` the game , you can see two characters 
            . ```Green character```(which is moving)
            . ```Red character```(still)
4. The Goal is to save collision of green and red character , for that we can jump up and move left and rigth Red character.
5. We use arrow keys to control red character to move , and save it from collison.
6. The challenge is speed of Green character is constantly increasing.
7. Game will be over once collide.

                  

